#inDinero Bootcamp

##Welcome

Welcome to the inDinero Bootcamp.

This bootcamp is intended to train prospective students, interns, junior developers and remain as an active resource for the core team.

The bootcamp will cover all topics required for a Full Stack Web Developer at inDinero. If you complete the course properly, you should be able to build a scalable web product and have the skills to maintain it.

##Curriculum

* Intro - Setup, Unix, datastructure and algorithms review, git
* Ruby - Basics, Network IO, blocks, scope, metaprogramming, regex
* Rails - MVC, ORM, routes, html, CSS, CRUD
* Javascript - scopes, jQuery, backbone
* Tests & process - Rspec, cucumber, scrums
* Server Ops - deployment, capistrano
* Projects


